quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,15,"Ndipo iwo, mwa akazi anu, amene achita chigololo, pezani mboni zokwanira zinayi zochokera pakati panu ndipo ngati iwo apereka umboni wotsimikiza, asungeni kunyumba zawo mpaka pamene imfa iwapeza kapena mpaka pamene Mulungu alamula kwa iwo njira ina"
  4,16,"Ndipo ngati anthu awiri achita chigololo pakati panu, alangeni onse awiri. Ngati iwo alapa ndi kusiya njira zawo zoipa, asiyeni. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi wa chisoni chosatha"
  4,17,Mulungu amavomera kulapa kwa amene achita zoipa mosazindikira ngati alapa mwamsanga. Ndi iwo amene Mulungu adzawakhululukira ndipo Mulungu ndi wodziwa ndiponso wanzeru
  4,18,"Kulibe phindu kulapa kwa iwo amene amachita zinthu zoipa mpaka pamene imfa imupeza wina wa iwo ndipo ati: “Tsopano ndalapa,” kapena kwa iwo amene amafa ali osakhulupirira. Kwa iwo Ife tawakonzera chilango chowawa"
  4,19,"oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Inu simuloledwa kulowa chokolo chokakamiza ndipo musawazunze ndi cholinga choti muwalande zina zimene mudawapatsa pokhapokha ngati achita chigololo. Ndipo khalani nawo mwa mtendere. Ngati simukuwafuna, mwina mungachide chinthu chimene Mulungu waikamo zabwino zambiri"